      "source_image": "IMG_0440.jpg"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "মামাইন্তে (-ইন্তে প্রত্যয়)",
      "source_page": 440,
      "source_image": "IMG_0440.jpg"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "মামারা",
